  "summary": {
    "as": "Passed House",
    "asOf": "2023-02-27",
    "date": "2023-03-06T19:01:23Z",
    "text": "Informing Consumers about Smart Devices Act\n\nThis bill requires manufacturers of internet-connected devices (e.g., smart appliances) that are equipped with a camera or microphone to disclose to consumers that a camera or microphone is part of the device.\n\nThe bill does not apply to mobile phones, laptops, or other devices that a consumer would reasonably expect to include a camera or microphone."
